# Imobi

Hacky companion app for cash games like Monopoly or Banco Imobili√°rio in a single* HTML file, allowing pay/recieve from a specific player, all players or bank.

All data is persisted in local storage. It is possible to drop this in a Android device and use as a companion for a tabletop game.

Right now, it includes Bulma and some icons from font-awesome.




* Icons not included in the file.

